Hand Made In The USA! 
Our stickers are custom, made to order, designed, cut, and shipped from our studio right here in the great state of Maine. We use only the highest quality ink and vinyl materials, 100% AMERICAN MADE and MADE TO LAST. Fully laminated with UV protection film that makes them incredibly durable, scratch-proof, waterproof, and weatherproof for years. 

Our graphic decals & sticker products are easy to apply and perfectly suited for any smooth surface such as a helmet, hard hat, bumper, toolbox, game console, motorcycle, scrapbook, window, kayak, canoe, RV, camper, yeti cooler, boat, wall, car, truck, laptop, surfboard, skateboard, snowboard, fridge, water bottle, or tumbler. Sizing & Colors: 
Sizes are approximate and are listed in inches as Width x Height ("). The height is proportional to the width. Colors may vary slightly from the actual sticker you receive. Since every computer screen is different with varying levels of accurate color calibration, slight variants can be expected.

FAST & FREE Shipping:
We ship all orders either the same day or next. We always ship within 24 hours unless your order is placed on the weekend or a holiday, then it’ll go out on the very next business day. Please note that standard first class mail does not have tracking. If your order is over $20.00, a tracking number will be provided. If your order is under $20.00, there will not be tracking information unless requested. (just message us). Your items will arrive to your mailbox either in a #10 white envelope or manila envelope from 207 THREADS in the return address. Please do not mistake this for junk mail. (it’s happened! :)

Return Policy / Exchanges / Refunds:
Returns are only granted if the decal is unused. We are not responsible for incorrect installation. HOWEVER… Customer satisfaction is our priority! If you’re unhappy with our products for any reason, please send us a message first before leaving negative feedback. I assure you that we will do everything we can to make things right and assure your ultimate satisfaction. We value your business and we don’t just want to sell you one sticker, we want you to be so happy with your purchase that you return for more and feel great about recommending us to others.

Custom Orders & Requests
If you have a unique design that you’d like created, or would like to order one of our existing designs in a different size or color, please message us anytime and we’ll make it happen for you!

Discover the classic charm of our Richardson 112 Old 1901 Vintage Maine Flag trucker hat with an originally designed leatherette patch that displays your love of the Original Maine Flag.

- Design: 6 Panel Structured Trucker Style
- Structured, Mid-Profile
- Multiple Color Combinations

Care Instructions: 
To maintain your hat's condition, hand wash it gently in cold water, targeting only the areas that need cleaning. Use a damp cloth for spot cleaning and avoid submerging the hat in water, especially around the patch. Avoid cleaning hats in washing machines and dishwashers to prevent damage.

Return and Exchange Policy: 
All of our hats are custom made to order. As with most small business craft sellers here on Etsy, we do not carry stock or inventory of our products like Amazon and the big box stores do, so thank you for understanding our no returns/no exchanges policy. However, please do reach out to us for assistance if you feel there might be a defect in your hat as we stand by the quality of our products and are always willing and open to fair resolutions for both parties. 

Delivery Terms: 
We remind our customers to ensure a secure drop-off location for packages. Once a package is marked as delivered, we cannot offer refunds for stolen or lost items post-delivery. In such cases, please understand it is up to the buyer to contact their local Post Office or specified delivery carrier for assistance.

This listing is for the romper only, but...
We also carry accessories and mom, dad , and sibling shirts all available in the "One Birthday" section of our shop.  You can find that here:
https://www.etsy.com/shop/2troubleboys?ref=simple-shop-header-name&listing_id=768848534&section_id=25625515

If no name is wanted please put "none" in the box.

Sizing information:
6 Month: Shoulder to between legs 14" . Shoulder to ankle 20".
9 Month: Shoulder to between legs 15". Shoulder to ankle 22.5".
12 Month: Shoulder to between legs 16". Shoulder to ankle 23.5".
18 Month: Shoulder to between legs 16.5". Shoulder to ankle 24.5".
2T: Shoulder to between legs 17.5". Shoulder to ankle 26"
3T: Shoulder to between legs 19". Shoulder to ankle. 29"
 
Based on our other rompers, we believe this romper runs a little small.  Please use measurements to ensure proper fit.

Measuring directions:
The best way to measure is to take an existing bodysuit and measure from the middle of the shoulder to the crotch area. Then compare to the measurements listed above.  If you are unsure, we always recommend sizing up. Make sure to take into account any growth that may take place if you order in advance.

Wanting the writing in a different color?  Please contact us for options!

Care instructions: 
Hand wash or machine wash on gentle cycle only
lay flat to dry or dry inside out on low only.
Do not use fabric softner or bleach.
